reviewText: My daughter loves the characters on this. She watches this one all year long! I even like it too ;)
My 5 year old granddaughter loves this DVD.
Bought as a gift for my granddaughter. She loves to watch the show, so I knew she would love watching this.

I bought this or my little sisters for Valentines Day. They both enjoyed every single episode and rewatched the movie more than once. So I was very happy that they enjoyed it. They said it's very cute and they loved it! Hopefully they'll make more movies so I can buy them another one.
My daughter loves this DVD. She has watched it over and over.
